            <fr:title text="geometric interpretation of perturbations">geometric interpretation of <fr:link href="/forest/hmlg-001C/" title="perturbation of chain complex" uri="https://trebor-huang.github.io/forest/hmlg-001C/" display-uri="hmlg-001C" type="local">perturbations</fr:link></fr:title>
          </fr:frontmatter>
          <fr:mainmatter>
            <html:p>
  For <fr:link href="/forest/hmlg-0013/" title="algebraic cellular complex" uri="https://trebor-huang.github.io/forest/hmlg-0013/" display-uri="hmlg-0013" type="local">ACCs</fr:link>, the effect of a perturbation is to “reconnect” the cells. But it may not create or delete cells, since the abelian groups are unchanged.
</html:p>
